Name: Wizard of Wyndmoor
About the game: Wizard of Wyndmoor is a wizard fantasy-survival game. Try and survive as long as you can with an onslaught of different enemies. Collect rings to level up and build your character. Enemies get stronger for each wave that comes to attack. There is no where to hide, the enemies will keep coming after you as your score goes up until your inescapably death! E Works on Windows, Mac (M1 NATIVE!), and Linux
